ges](landing-pages-sales-funnels.html)\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"13\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"14\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      - [Training](training.html)\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"15\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"16\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      - [Get a Quote](contact.html\\\" class=\\\"nav-cta)\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"17\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"18\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"19\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"20\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"21\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"22\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"23\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"24\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      Digital Marketing · 10 min read\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"25\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      # WhatsApp Marketing for Nigerian Businesses: Complete 2025 Guide\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"26\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"27\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      By Hephzibah Media Team · Published January 10, 2025\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"28\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      90 million Nigerians use WhatsApp. It's where your customers already are. Yet most Nigerian businesses treat WhatsApp as a support channel, not a revenue driver. This guide shows you how to build a broadcast list, automate sales sequences, and drive conversions without becoming annoying.\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"29\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"30\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"31\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"32\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"33\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"34\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## The Difference: Broadcast Lists vs Group Chats\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"35\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"36\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"37\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Broadcast lists let you send messages to many customers who each think you're messaging them personally. They can reply, but replies go to your personal inbox. This is GDPR-friendly and doesn't feel spammy. Never use groups for marketing  it's immediately annoying and violates WhatsApp's Terms of Service.\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"38\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"39\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Building Your WhatsApp Broadcast List\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"40\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"41\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"42\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Start by asking: 'Add me to WhatsApp for updates/offers.' Link to WhatsApp from your website, Instagram bio, and email signature. Use QR codes in physical locations. Ask in-store customers: 'Text HELLO to +234 907 778 0156 for exclusive offers.' Tools: Twilio (API), WhatsApp Business API, or manually if <1,000 contacts.\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"43\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"44\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Crafting Broadcast Messages That Convert\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"45\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"46\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"47\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Limit to 34 messages weekly. Message TuesdaysThursdays 10am2pm WAT. Never send at night or weekends. Use emoji (??, ?, ??) but sparingly. Always include a clear CTA: 'Reply SHOP to browse our new collection.' Track replies and manually respond  WhatsApp doesn't have open rates, but reply rates tell you what resonates.\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"48\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"49\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Automating Sales Sequences with Chatbots\\r\"}],\"$L2\",\"$L3\",\"$L4\",\"$L5\",\"$L6\",\"$L7\",\"$L8\",\"$L9\",\"$La\",\"$Lb\",\"$Lc\",\"$Ld\",\"$Le\",\"$Lf\",\"$L10\",\"$L11\",\"$L12\",\"$L13\",\"$L14\",\"$L15\",\"$L16\",\"$L17\",\"$L18\",\"$L19\",\"$L1a\",\"$L1b\",\"$L1c\",\"$L1d\",\"$L1e\",\"$L1f\",\"$L20\",\"$L21\",\"$L22\",\"$L23\",\"$L24\",\"$L25\",\"$L26\",\"$L27\",\"$L28\",\"$L29\",\"$L2a\",\"$L2b\",\"$L2c\",\"$L2d\",\"$L2e\",\"$L2f\",\"$L30\",\"$L31\",\"$L32\",\"$L33\",\"$L34\",\"$L35\",\"$L36\",\"$L37\",\"$L38\",\"$L39\",\"$L3a\",\"$L3b\",\"$L3c\",\"$L3d\",\"$L3e\",\"$L3f\",\"$L40\",\"$L41\",\"$L42\",\"$L43\",\"$L44\",\"$L45\",\"$L46\",\"$L47\",\"$L48\",\"$L49\",\"$L4a\",\"$L4b\",\"$L4c\",\"$L4d\",\"$L4e\",\"$L4f\",\"$L50\"]}]]}],null,\"$L51\"]}],\"isPartial\":false,\"staleTime\":300,\"varyParams\":null,\"buildId\":\"i9Cf0qMmt9f6Hl-9FDnLU\"}\n2:[\"$\",\"br\",\"50\",{}]\n3:[\"$\",\"br\",\"51\",{}]\n4:[\"$\",\"p\",\"52\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Tools like Botpress, ManyChat, or Twilio Studio let you build flows: 1) Customer replies 'SHOP' 2) Bot sends product list with images 3) Bot asks 'Which product interest you?' 4) Bot collects order details 5) Your team fulfills. This scales without hiring people to manually reply 1,000 messages daily.\\r\"}]\n5:[\"$\",\"br\",\"53\",{}]\n6:[\"$\",\"p\",\"54\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Common Mistakes Nigerian Businesses Make\\r\"}]\n7:[\"$\",\"br\",\"55\",{}]\n8:[\"$\",\"br\",\"56\",{}]\n9:[\"$\",\"p\",\"57\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Sending the same message to all contacts (personalise!), not respecting quiet hours (11pm8am), including too many links in one message (WhatsApp flags this as spam), and ignoring replies (customers feel ignored). Fix these four and your response rate jumps 60%.\\r\"}]\na:[\"$\",\"br\",\"58\",{}]\nb:[\"$\",\"p\",\"59\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Measuring What Works\\r\"}]\nc:[\"$\",\"br\",\"60\",{}]\nd:[\"$\",\"br\",\"61\",{}]\ne:[\"$\",\"p\",\"62\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"WhatsApp doesn't provide analytics. Create a Google Form link that customers tap to 'confirm order'  this gives you click tracking. Or use UTM parameters on links: 'https://yoursite.com?utm_source=whatsapp&utm_campaign=jan_sale.' Track conversions by asking 'Where did you hear about us?' at checkout.\\r\"}]\nf:[\"$\",\"br\",\"63\",{}]\n10:[\"$\",\"br\",\"64\",{}]\n11:[\"$\",\"br\",\"65\",{}]\n12:[\"$\",\"br\",\"66\",{}]\n13:[\"$\",\"br\",\"67\",{}]\n14:[\"$\",\"p\",\"68\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"    ## Ready for Growth?\\r\"}]\n15:[\"$\",\"br\",\"69\",{}]\n16:[\"$\",\"br\",\"70\",{}]\n17:[\"$\",\"p\",\"71\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Let our team audit your current marketing strategy and show you exactly what's holding you back.\\r\"}]\n18:[\"$\",\"br\",\"72\",{}]\n19:[\"$\",\"p\",\"73\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"    [Start Your Free Audit](contact.html\\\" class=\\\"btn-primary)\\r\"}]\n1a:[\"$\",\"br\",\"74\",{}]\n1b:[\"$\",\"br\",\"75\",{}]\n1c:[\"$\",\"br\",\"76\",{}]\n1d:[\"$\",\"br\",\"77\",{}]\n1e:[\"$\",\"br\",\"78\",{}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"p\",\"79\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"        Hephzibah Media\\r\"}]\n20:[\"$\",\"br\",\"80\",{}]\n21:[\"$\",\"p\",\"81\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Nigeria's premium Digital Marketing, Tech & Print Agency. Building brands that dominate from Ogere, Ogun State.\\r\"}]\n22:[\"$\",\"br\",\"82\",{}]\n23:[\"$\",\"p\",\"83\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"        Old Ode Road, Along Ogere Tollgate, Ogere, Nigeria\\r\"}]\n24:[\"$\",\"br\",\"84\",{}]\n25:[\"$\",\"br\",\"85\",{}]\n26:[\"$\",\"p\",\"86\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"        Services\\r\"}]\n27:[\"$\",\"br\",\"87\",{}]\n28:[\"$\",\"p\",\"88\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"          - [Web Design](web-design.html)\\r\"}]\n29:[\"$\",\"br\",\"89\",{}]\n2a:[\"$\",\"p\",\"90\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"          - [Digital Marketing](digital-marketing.html)\\r\"}]\n2b:[\"$\",\"br\",\"91\",{}]\n2c:[\"$\",\"p\",\"92\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"          - [SEO](seo.html)\\r\"}]\n2d:[\"$\",\"br\",\"93\",{}]\n2e:[\"$\",\"p\",\"94\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"          - [Graphics Design](graphics-design.html)\\r\"}]\n2f:[\"$\",\"br\",\"95\",{}]\n30:[\"$\",\"br\",\"96\",{}]\n31:[\"$\",\"br\",\"97\",{}]\n32:[\"$\",\"br\",\"98\",{}]\n33:[\"$\",\"p\",\"99\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"        Resources\\r\"}]\n34:[\"$\",\"br\",\"100\",{}]\n35:[\"$\",\"p\",\"101\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"          - [Blog](blog.html)\\r\"}]\n36:[\"$\",\"br\",\"102\",{}]\n37:[\"$\",\"p\",\"103\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"          - [Portfolio](portfolio.html)\\r\"}]\n38:[\"$\",\"b